<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870515-0162 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business:Norcen Energy Resources Ltd.</HL><DD> 05/15/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> T.NCNBOND MARKET NEWS (BON) </IN><TEXT>   NORCEN ENERGY RESOURCES LTD., a Calgary, Alberta-based oil and gas company, said it completed a sale of $150 million (Canadian) of debentures convertible into common at $25 a share. Proceeds will be used to reduce short-term debt. The debentures pay 5% interest and aren't redeemable before May 15, 1992. </TEXT></DOC>